ARM: SAMSUNG: remove unused SAMSUNG_GPIOLIB_4BIT Kconfig parameter

This removes the SAMSUNG_GPIOLIB_4BIT Kconfig parameter,
which was no longer used anywhere in the source code
and Makefiles.

